        public Race()
        This is the constructor method of the Race class.

        The cost of the ticket will be generated by a random number. The date and time of the order will be obtained through the LocalDateTime() function. nameDriver Name of the assigned driver. nameClient Name of the client who requested the service. startingPoint Location of the starting point where the cab picks up the client. arrivalPoint Location of the arrival point where the cab drops off the client. passengerCount The number of passengers entering the cab.
